<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <title></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .button {
      display: block;
      width: 200px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }

    .manual-link {
      word-break: break-all;
      color: #0066cc;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666666;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="header">
  <h1><%= t(:blog_name) %></h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
  <p>Hello <%= @email_subscriber.email %>,</p>

  <p>Thank you for subscribing to <%= t(:blog_name) %>!</p>

  <p><%= t('subscription.confirmation.instructions') %></p>

  <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>" class="button"><%= t('subscription.confirmation.button') %></a>

  <p>If the button above doesn't work, please copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>

  <p class="manual-link"><%= @confirmation_url %></p>

  <p>After confirming your subscription, you will start receiving email notifications when new content is published.</p>

  <p><%= t('subscription.confirmation.expiration_notice') %></p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> <%= t(:blog_name) %>. All rights reserved.</p>
  <p>If you did not request this subscription, please ignore this email or contact us to let us know.</p>
  <p>This email was sent to <%= @email_subscriber.email %>.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
